description:
Necessary Evil is a collection of several different stories that feature various villains in the DCU. The stories give a short preview of the many popular villains that reside in the DCU, along with a small biography to explain their origin.

The purpose of Necessary Evil is to act as a companion guide to go alongside the documentary DVD produced by DC Entertainment.

The star of the smashing hit game, Cut the Rope, now has a new comic book series! See the amazing fun story of Om Nom and his friends unfold! description:
EVERY GREAT HERO HAS A BEGINNING… Some of those beginnings are even great

For WILL POWER, the unique set of circumstances that bring about his heroic journey will become his LEGEND! It will make him the most powerful superhero that ever lived, that is, if he can just make it past HOME ROOM and MATH CLASS!

You will not be disappointed in this hero’s classic tale of self-realization and fun filled heroic birth! THE LEGEND OF WILL POWER is a throwback story, much like the classic comic books from the mid 90′s. You will feel like comics are fun again as you dive deeper and deeper into the surprisingly rich mythology that is THE LEGEND OF WILL POWER!

DO YOU KNOW THE LEGEND?
name: The Legend Of Will Power

deck: THE POWERVERSE CHRONICLES is a spotlight series created and written by Vince White and published by Primal Paper Comics. The series explores the new comic universe that exist inside and outside the pages of The Legend Of Will Power™ comic book series. Each issues highlights a new heroes or villain from the "Powerverse", a name coin to describe the Will Power universe.
